title: Mof Chef Cleaner Powder, Heavy Duty Grease Remover, Powerful Kitchen All-Purpose Powder Cleaner, Strong Foam Rust Removal Kitchen Cleaning Powder, Stubborn Grease & Grime Remover（500g）
features: Heavy Degreaser Cleaner: The kitchen multi-purpose cleaning powder can provide you with the ultimate cleaning power, easily remove the stubborn oil and rust left in the kitchen, and restore your kitchen to its original state
